{"id":"gold_0017","question":"Summarize the recurring themes in the support tickets about noisy or excessive alerting.","answer":"Several customers report high alert volume, especially spikes during shift-handoff windows, which saturates on-call staff. A common ask is to tune or suppress the noisy alerts, and in a few accounts the alert fatigue ties into renewal or procurement pressure.","match_type":"judge","retrieval_evaluation":"required","relevant_ids":{"artifacts":["art_095b99836169","art_0a135c689c08","art_17abbddc8e1c","art_188354354875","art_2420588c7e8d","art_25fac9f564e7","art_2a2227a894e2","art_2c74d2b4b2e4","art_30819100b117","art_3dd0473bff8c","art_49ed2e9ef596","art_49f5fae5a1cf","art_4a2b3d30f2d2","art_50987b3f2b98","art_57ab871c2b35","art_599ab3ce9cc8","art_59bc3aae72e6","art_696c07fdb010","art_6c9446a04e8d","art_6f285c2f3219","art_760df143a1e2","art_769fb1a3b020","art_8254b9cf5801","art_873073298cc9","art_87ce7dc50339","art_9507c03d9d65","art_973a6b38fe0c","art_9a8845b33c9e","art_a9d51da1b57b","art_ac0f6823bd92","art_bcc36979e170","art_e89e8accadd2","art_f92d6a99f322","art_fcc001e817e5","art_ffa7143fb822"]}}
{"id":"gold_0018","question":"What pain points come up repeatedly across our at-risk customer accounts?","answer":"At-risk accounts repeatedly show noisy or excessive alerting, remediation and rollback issues after misconfigurations, and escalations. These pain points recur across several different customers, not just one account.","match_type":"judge","retrieval_evaluation":"required","relevant_ids":{"artifacts":["art_0927b1cbb7f4","art_3ba29fe1e026","art_50987b3f2b98","art_6be1b68b59cb","art_8b0063fbb3cb","art_a0ed9f935d3e","art_cbfb5f92862c","art_cc1d06976a22","art_fbed53e40d47","art_fc6c465c3c59"]}}
{"id":"gold_0019","question":"Give me your read on BeaconOps as a competitor, its strengths and where it's weak.","answer":"BeaconOps's main strengths are fast agent onboarding and a large playbook library. Its main weaknesses are limited retention controls and less emphasis on compliance exports.","match_type":"judge","retrieval_evaluation":"required","relevant_ids":{"competitors":["cmp_15f3d499e5c7"],"artifacts":["art_0927b1cbb7f4","art_1290f5ea8c04","art_1e14a6be3a7f","art_2432dccbcdcb","art_2a33ad2fe047","art_3138b5cfc288","art_4b144e303af5","art_4f1200ae5a1f","art_9ae897b5abc3","art_ba141dc7febd","art_e6d67dfd5f1a"]}}
